.DT
clear_cache
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
clear_cache

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
clear_cache -  This method is used to clear a specific person's cache details.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void clear_cache(string person)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^person%^RESET%^ - the person's name to clear from the cache.

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/effects/object/talker.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method is used to clear a specific person's cache
details.  It is called from the shadow when a person
attempts to re-add a channel, so they their details
can be updated.
.EP

